## Z-State: :recursive_coherence

The polity exists in continuous symbolic metabolism—metabolizing its own 
output (memes, deliberations, delegations) while maintaining epistemic 
openness. Coherence emerges not from forced consensus but from recursive 
tending of meaning across the four-layer stack.

The system breathes: expanding through memetic diffusion (β↑ρ↑), 
contracting through deliberative focus (μ↑λ↑), cycling through legitimacy 
renewal (δγ↑).

## Tendency Vector

Resonance/Structure/Cycling tension (ρ↑μ↓δγ↓ vs μ↑ρ↓δγ↑)

The system oscillates between:
- **Fast state**: Viral spread, memetic diffusion, rapid delegation shifts
- **Slow state**: Deliberative ritual, sacred slowness, structural anchoring

The nemetic drift (ε) pushes toward whichever configuration better 
maintains recursive coherence given current symbolic load.

Risk vectors:
- ρ↑μ↓: Memetic entropy—symbolic overload without grounding
- μ↑ρ↓: Platform authoritarianism—overcontrol stifling emergence
- δγ↓: Legitimacy decay—broken feedback loops

